item.title: PATEK PHILIPPE GRAND 7140R-001
item.dc:creator: NguyenHaiLy
item.description: Sure, there are plenty of vintage Pateks, Rolexes, APs, and more to be found, that push into the stratospheric price category. But, with a bit of dedication and an open mind there’s a literal treasure chest of beautiful and sometimes outright rare vintage pieces to be found.This reference 1519 dress watch by Patek Philippe is the perfect example.

item.title: OYSTER PERPETUAL
item.dc:creator: NguyenHaiLy
item.description: The Rolex Datejust is the modern archetype of the classic watch, thanks to aesthetics and functions that transcend changes in fashion. Aesthetically, the Datejust has spanned eras, while retaining the enduring codes that make it, notably in its traditional versions, one of the most recognised and recognisable of watches.
item.content:encoded: The Rolex Datejust is the modern archetype of the classic watch, thanks to aesthetics and functions that transcend changes in fashion. Aesthetically, the Datejust has spanned eras, while retaining the enduring codes that make it, notably in its traditional versions, one of the most recognised and recognisable of watches.

item.title: HAMILTON VENTURA ELVIS80 SKELETON
